Interface TreeNodeVisitor

public interface TreeNodeVisitor

Instances of TreeNodeVisitor are supplied to TreeTraverser objects.

A TreeTraverser will call visit() for each TreeNode that it comes across during the traversal of a BinaryTree. Any functionality that is required of a traversal, is therefore best implemented in the visit() method.
